- Sends `{ query, thread_id: activeThreadId, user_id: currentUserId }` instead of `{ query }`
- After first message in a new session, calls `loadSessions()` to refresh the sidebar with the auto-generated name

**On page load:**
1. Call `loadSessions()` to populate sidebar
2. Auto-call `createSession()` so the user starts with a fresh thread immediately

